          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Distorted-wave Born approximation (DWBA) calculations",
                "were performed with the code PTOLEMY. For the four",
                "lowest-lying states, the agreement between the",
                "experimental angular distributions and the DWBA",
                "calculation confirms previous momentum assignments.",
                "For the unbound states, a binding energy of 200 keV",
                "for the transferred neutron was assumed in a",
                "\"quasi-bound\" approach. The 4.52(4)- and 5.43(4)-MeV",
                "resonances have fitted widths Gamma = 220(80) keV and",
                "Gamma < 90 keV, and were tentatively assigned l = 1,2",
                "and l = 3, respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
